rnd_str: Random assignment by strata

Source: R/rnd_str.R
rnd_str.Rd

Take a dataset and assign treatment by a specified stratum

rnd_str(df, strata, id)

Arguments

df

a dataframe, containing strata variable
strata

a column in df naming the stratification variable, can be character or numeric
id

A variable identify unit of randomization

Value

dataframe with new column assigning treatment

Examples

df <- jumble::ACTG175
rnd_str(df, symptom, pidnum)
